                    "detailed_description": "Pantai Cenang is the heart of Langkawi's tourism scene. The beach itself is a beautiful expanse of white sand, perfect for sunbathing and swimming. It offers a plethora of water sports, including jet-skiing and banana boating. The main road running parallel to the beach is lined with a diverse array of shops, duty-free outlets, spas, and restaurants catering to all tastes. Attractions like the Underwater World Langkawi are also located here. As evening falls, the beachfront bars and restaurants come alive, offering stunning sunset views and a vibrant atmosphere.",
